column5: Being some what new to health care, I have noticed something interesting. Tracking, keeping track of all kinds of information is a contant in this field.I was wondering how many camps, outposts and fly-ins get people from WC reports at their lakes? The next item would be how many outfitters monitor WC for reports and recomendations? Next item, maybe I am thinking way to much about my first year of two trips North!??
there are many outfitters on WC that watch to posts
